  classification stage after inserting a message, failing to find a trigger
  row, observing target-agent responses containing the hash, and seeing the
  expected proof file.
- The bridge daemon consumes existing agent_triggers rows. It does not create
  trigger rows for new messages, so there is no bridge trigger-insertion
  try/catch to audit for this missing row.


